des:
There’s no need to go to the switch to adjust you home light - just talk to Alexa on your Amazon Echo. 

After connecting Alexa to your Conectoz products in a few simple steps:
(1). Download our "Conectoz" app in android or ios app market;
(2). Register one Conectoz account in our "Conectoz" app;
(3). You need to have some Conectoz devices in hand;
(4). Configure these devices in our Conectoz app and change appropriate name for your devices which will be used in "Conectoz" skills;
(5). Download Amazon "Alexa" app from android,ios or Amazon app market;
(6). Configure Echo with "Alexa" app;
(7). Search "Conectoz" skill from the "Alexa" app skills category;
(8). Click Enable skill of "Conectoz", and you'll be navigated to Conectoz login page;
(9). Input your Conectoz account username and password, you'll be redirect to the success page;
(10). Now all setup is finished. 
You can enjoy the voice control on your home devices like these:
“Alexa, turn on kitchen light"
“Alexa, turn off kitchen light"
“Alexa, dim livingroom light"
“Alexa, brighten livingroom light"
“Alexa, set the livingroom light to 20 percent"
“Alexa, set bedroom light to Blue"

If you have any problem when you use this skill, you can contact us in our Website www.conectoz.com.br/contato
